17 年 Ultimate 推出以来价格首次上涨。微软将价格上涨归咎于“竞争条件”的变化，但这也反映了战略的演变。微软及其竞争对手索尼都<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/xbox-game-pass-ps-plus-premium-comparison-video-152033098.html">越来越依赖订阅来</a>获取收入，而 Game Pass Ultimate 的涨价可能会在这方面有所帮助。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/xbox-game-pass-ultimate-1-deal-is-back-for-new-users-194212213.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/xbox-game-pass-ultimate-1-deal-is-back-for-new-users-194212213.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4982a444-6c5e-4d46-a1c5-57887356cafd</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 19:42:12 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688758933</ingested><modified> 2023-07-07T19:42:17+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/f8d7ff00-7f6d-11eb-bfbf-57b7e2dd56d8" width="1800"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/f8d7ff00-7f6d-11eb-bfbf-57b7e2dd56d8" width="1800"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Aaron Souppouris/Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Microsoft Xbox Series X with Series S and P